data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of NW Tucson, where tranquility meets modern comfort. This updated 4 bedroom, 2 bath home sits proudly on a sprawling lot with no HOA. Step inside, and you're struck by the spaciousness and warmth of the interior. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for both entertaining guests and everyday living.The living room is bathed in natural light pouring in through large windows, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Imagine cozy evenings by the fireplace, enjoying the company of loved ones or simply unwinding. Step through the sliding glass doors onto your expansive backyard oasis, where endless possibilities await.  Plenty of room for RV's or toys! Schedule your showing today!
